294
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,119
Hear, hear.

295
00:17:06,359 --> 00:17:07,079
Exactly.

296
00:17:07,280 --> 00:17:08,199
I understand.

297
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:09,760
