♪Night is when the Day sleeps♪

387
00:24:25,894 --> 00:24:29,160
♪You are a part of me♪

388
00:24:30,154 --> 00:24:33,839
♪With a merry start,
don't worry about a sorrowful end♪

389
00:24:34,210 --> 00:24:37,420
♪A full moon will be more intertwined♪

390
